</a>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='meta m4'>
14 talks
&bull;
<span class='meta__val'>3h 43m</span>
</div>
<div class='p4'>We need to talk about war. These powerful, crucial talks come from soldiers, politicians, journalists and others who've seen the reality of war firsthand.</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='m2'>
<h4 class='h7 m3'>The road to peace</h4>
<div class='row row-skinny row-oh-2up'>
<div class='col'>
<a href='/playlists/22/the_road_to_peace'>
<span class="thumb thumb--square"><span class="thumb__sizer"><span class="thumb__tugger"><img alt="" class=" thumb__image" play="false" src="https://tedcdnpi-a.akamaihd.net/r/tedcdnpf-a.akamaihd.net/images/playlists/the_road_to_peace.jpg?quality=89&amp;w=256" /><span class="thumb__aligner"></span></span></span></span>
</a>
</div>
<div class='col'>
<div class='meta m4'>
10 talks
&bull;
<span class='meta__val'>2h 24m</span>
</div>
<div class='p4'>Peace. It's humanity's eternal, elusive dream. These speakers offer inspired ideas, practical advice and real-world examples from around the globe of how it just might be attainable.</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
